      • getPrefs

        public java.lang.Object getPrefs(java.lang.String sharedPreferences,
                        java.lang.String key,
                        int type,
                        Context context)
        Method to get values in Shared Preferences. It retrieves different values depending on input parameters. Returns retrieved value if all is fine else it returns a String "ERROR".
        Example usage:
        String s = getPrefs(SmsAlarm.SHARED_PREF, ACK_NUMBER_KEY, 1, this.context) , this will retrieve a string(type = 1) from key ACK_NUMBER_KEY and with the given context.
        Parameters:
        sharedPreferences - SharedPreferences from which the values are retrieved from
        key - Key in which Shared Preference is stored
        type - Different type of values is retrieved from Shared Preferences, indicated by this value. 0 = Integer, 1 = String, 2 = Boolean and 3 = List of Strings
        context - Context from which the Shared Preferences should be retrieved
        Returns:
        Returns an object with the retrieved values. This object can be an instance of Integer, String, Boolean or a List of Strings
        Throws:
        JSONException - if an error occur retrieving String from JSON Array
        See Also:
        PreferencesHandler(), getInstance(), getSHARED_PREF(), getNOT_KEY(), getPRIMARY_LISTEN_NUMBER_KEY(), getSECONDARY_LISTEN_NUMBERS_KEY(), getPRIMARY_MESSAGE_TONE_KEY(), getSECONDARY_MESSAGE_TONE_KEY(), getMESSAGE_KEY(), getFULL_MESSAGE_KEY(), getENABLE_ACK_KEY(), getACK_NUMBER_KEY(), getUSE_OS_SOUND_SETTINGS_KEY(), getLARM_TYPE_KEY(), getPLAY_TONE_TWICE_KEY(), getENABLE_SMS_ALARM_KEY(), getFIRE_DEPARTMENT_KEY(), setPrefs(String, String, Object, Context)

      • setPrefs

        public void setPrefs(java.lang.String sharedPreferences,
            java.lang.String key,
            java.lang.Object object,
            Context context)
        Method to set values to Shared Preferences. It sets different values of different instances depending on input parameters.
        Example usage:
        setPrefs(SmsAlarm.SHARED_PREF, ACKNUMBER_KEY, "0457 0000 000", this.context
        Parameters:
        sharedPreferences - SharedPreferences from which the values are retrieved from
        key - Key in which Shared Preference is stored
        object - Object to be stored to Shared Preferences, supported instances are Integer, String, Boolean and List
        context - Context from which the Shared Preferences should be retrieved
        See Also:
        PreferencesHandler(), getInstance(), getSHARED_PREF(), getNOT_KEY(), getPRIMARY_LISTEN_NUMBER_KEY(), getSECONDARY_LISTEN_NUMBERS_KEY(), getPRIMARY_MESSAGE_TONE_KEY(), getSECONDARY_MESSAGE_TONE_KEY(), getMESSAGE_KEY(), getFULL_MESSAGE_KEY(), getENABLE_ACK_KEY(), getACK_NUMBER_KEY(), getUSE_OS_SOUND_SETTINGS_KEY(), getLARM_TYPE_KEY(), getPLAY_TONE_TWICE_KEY(), getENABLE_SMS_ALARM_KEY(), getFIRE_DEPARTMENT_KEY(), getPrefs(String, String, int, Context), setPrefs(String, String, Object, Context)
